  "detailed_description": "The main objective in this game is to find your way out. Look for hints, notes or anything you could find in order to find the way out.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCurrent features:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* Atmosphere based game-play<br />\r\n* Story driven puzzles<br />\r\n* Different endings (depending on what path you choose)<br />\r\n* Random encounters<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe would also love to heard a feedback from you. For that, please refer to our community forums! Oculus Rift support will be coming within next two months.",
